metadata.name: Back Home The Future
metadata.description:
weak with nearly fail ... little hope out there
then returning home

the future is unpredictable but the hometown might not be cruel

this Moody's Village is still complicated ... leading the town by Bear Warrior and guarding by Stone Dragon

everything not be the same ... home's been changed!! lots of hope and mist here

here now accepts various Crypto Coins and also Alien Wallets ... this town's been rated as five stars from Alien Tourists, they love to visit the HUB-Station for Galaxy Migration of Whale-Floral ... yes Whale! Well Well ... Welcome Back Home The Future
